name: attn. hours - range
query:
SELECT
   COUNT(`tabCourse Schedule`.student_group) as "CS6551 (Total Hours):select:150"  
FROM
  `tabCourse Schedule`
WHERE
  (`tabCourse Schedule`.schedule_date BETWEEN '2018-07-28' AND '2018-08-25') and
  `tabCourse Schedule`.student_group = 'CS6551/B.Tech in Information Technology/A/2018-19 (Sem5)'
